35
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,640
Why were you laughing in your dream?

36
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,680
Who did you dream of?

37
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,680
Anyway, it's not you.

38
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,640
Is it Secretary Chen

39
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,600
or your meddlesome boss?

40
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,280
Why suddenly bring Mr. Meng up?

41
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,680
You said

42
