50
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,920
I have just ten meters to go.

51
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,880
See you at the office.

52
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,400
Drive.

53
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,000
What's up with him today?

54
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,880
Ye Ran,

55
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,560
