56
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,480
Was it because you overheard

57
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,520
my conversation with Ye Dang?

58
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,400
I'm sorry.

59
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,040
There's nothing to apologize for.

60
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,760
Liking someone

61
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,440
isn't something you can control.

62
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,240
You don't like me.

63
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,440
It's not your fault.

64
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,040
But I shouldn't have accepted you

65
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,200
without confirming

66
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,400
who I really liked.

67
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,200
I made you feel so bad.

68
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,720
You must have been upset yesterday.

69
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,440
I'm really sorry.

70
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,720
I was upset.

71
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,480
But not as much as you think.

72
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,920
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

73
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,800
Ye Ran,

74
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,800
you'll definitely meet someone

75
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,040
better than me in the future.

76
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,720
If you need anything,

77
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,360
just ask.

78
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,200
But you should worry about yourself first.

79
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,000
Ye Dang
is much harder to pursue than me.

80
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,680
Here's Ye Dang's number.

81
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,320
That's all I can do for you.

82
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,240
Unfaithful man.

83
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,880
Thanks.

84
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,440
Oh,

85
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,240
