89
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,040
There's something

90
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,440
I need to tell you.

91
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:16,060
(President's Office, Shanghe Garment Group)

92
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,360
Actually,

93
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,880
