94
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,320
There you are.

95
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,760
Lisa asked me to get you to sign this.

96
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,880
(She even found an excuse.)

97
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,320
(How cute.)

98
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,000
Mr. Meng,

99
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,360
