100
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,160
Take it.

101
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,320
Are both cups for me?

102
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,040
I bought them specially for you.

103
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,920
This umbrella isn't actually mine.

104
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,000
It's Mr. Memg's.

105
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,600
Two years ago,
he asked me to give it to you.

106
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,600
He also covered it up for you

107
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,210
